long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Finally GB Browser 4.7 is out and you can use it. The team has been working on the new logo for a while now to make it simple and elegant and also finally a name change from Gigabyte Browser to GB Browser. Our Team will try and not delay the updates like for the past month there has been no update but this might be the biggest one yet.

Also a new thing that might surprise you all the team has extended with another person working along side me on the core team. The Owner or Random Dev whose browser you can find down below named Prachet Sinha.
